Package org.hibernate.internal

Interface CoreMessageLogger

All Superinterfaces:
org.jboss.logging.BasicLogger
@MessageLogger(projectCode="HHH") @ValidIdRange(min=2, max=20000) @Internal public interface CoreMessageLogger extends org.jboss.logging.BasicLogger
The jboss-logging MessageLogger for the hibernate-core module. It reserves message ids ranging from 00001 to 10000 inclusively.

New messages must be added after the last message defined to ensure message codes are unique.
